Class Polygon

  • java.lang.Object
    • Polygon
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Rectangle, Triangle

    public abstract class Polygon
extends java.lang.Object
    class outlining methods of all polygons includes both graphical properties such as stroke width and fill/outline colours, and shape properties such as number of points and coordinates of points
